The Board of Almshouse Governors, not to be outdone by- Congress or the Legislature, has hesitated ever since the new Board came together,- in regard to the choice of President, and only settled its troubles on Saturday night. Meetings were held on Wednesday and Thursday, and a third on Saturday finished the business.
